@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #F7FCFF
    BorderColor #88BBDD
    FontSize 12
}
note over App, VFS
VFS三大操作集合划分规则
1.super_operations：整个文件系统生命周期(挂载/卸载/块管理)
2.inode_operations：不依赖fd，操作inode、dentry、目录、链接、改名删除
3.file_operations：open拿到fd后，读写/偏移/刷盘/关闭/mmap
end note

box "用户态 系统调用" #LightYellow
participant App
end box

box "VFS内核层" #LightCyan
participant SuperOps as "super_operations\n文件系统全局"
participant InodeOps as "inode_operations\ninode/dentry管理"
participant FileOps as "file_operations\n已打开文件IO"
end box

'=========super_operations 调用链路=========
App -> SuperOps: mount/umount/statfs
note right of SuperOps: mount挂载、卸载、超级块维护、磁盘块统计

'=========inode_operations 全量操作=========
App -> InodeOps: create/mkdir
App -> InodeOps: lookup(路径查找)
App -> InodeOps: link(硬链接)/symlink(软链接)
App -> InodeOps: unlink/rmdir
App -> InodeOps: rename
App -> InodeOps: readlink/setattr
note right of InodeOps: 全部不需要open，无fd参与，操纵目录项&inode属性

'=========file_operations 全量操作=========
App -> FileOps: open(后半段)/read/write
App -> FileOps: lseek/fsync/close/mmap
note right of FileOps: 必须经过open获取fd，操作打开后的文件实例struct file
@enduml